    22     24.7 MiB     24.7 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     24.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     24.8 MiB      0.1 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     24.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     24.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     24.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     25.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    29     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     25.8 MiB     25.8 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     25.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     26.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    24     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     25.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    24     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     26.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     26.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     26.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    30     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35                             
    36     26.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    30     27.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct

    33     27.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     27.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    31     27.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35                             
    36     27.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    24     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     27.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    31     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     27.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    24     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     27.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    29     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     27.8 MiB     27.8 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     27.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    27     27.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)

    30     27.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     27.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    24     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     28.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    30     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35                             
    36     28.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    28     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    26     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    31     28.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    24     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     28.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    31     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    24     28.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35                             
    36     28.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    31     30.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    24     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     30.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    31     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    24     31.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     31.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     31.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)

    27     31.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)

    31     32.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    24     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     32.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)

    27     32.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)

    22     31.7 MiB     31.7 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     31.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     31.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    31     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     31.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct

    22     32.1 MiB     32.1 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     32.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     32.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     32.6 MiB     32.6 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     32.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     32.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     32.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35

    22     33.0 MiB     33.0 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     33.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     33.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    30     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct

    32     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))

    35                             
    36     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     33.2 MiB     33.2 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    29     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)

    36     33.3 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     33.4 MiB     33.4 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     33.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.5 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    31     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)

    24     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     33.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    30     33.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)

    22     33.8 MiB     33.8 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     33.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     33.9 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    31     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.0 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    29     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.1 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)

    22     34.2 MiB     34.2 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)

    36     34.2 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    30     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.4 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)

    22     34.6 MiB     34.6 MiB   @profile
    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):
    24     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       uid = int(uid)
    25     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)
    33     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       f = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + str(pwd) + str(ct))
    34     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       smart_card = (auth_params, tp, ltk, compute_one_way_hash(k), f)
    35                             
    36     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       store_user_data(biom_file, smart_card, uid)
    37     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       print("Successfully registered user: ", uid)
    38     34.6 MiB      0.0 MiB       return 0

    25     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
    29     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       kcw = util.encode(k)
    30     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       ltk = kcw ^ ct
    31     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       pwd = compute_one_way_hash(str(uid) + k + pw)
    32     34.7 MiB      0.0 MiB       auth_params = register_user(uid, pwd)

    23                             def register(uid, pw, biom_file):

    25     34.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       biom = util.load_biometric(biom_file)
    26     34.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       tp = numpy.random.rand(4)
    27     34.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       ct = compute_cancellable_template(biom, tp)
    28     34.8 MiB      0.0 MiB       k = str(uuid.uuid1())
